title: Win10_1511_1_English_x64.img
description:
This is how it was made: I downloaded the Win10_1511_1_English_x64.iso from Microsoft's website and used the Windows 7/8 USB Installation making windows tool to put it on USB. After which, I used dd for windows and read 4.5Gbytes exactly from the flash device to an image file. Windows now only has tools to create media, so this may be helpful to some of you.

It says there is no seeds although I am seeding encrypted and the tracker is my private one.
